{"tid":2388974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於BNO，分享下支那人民既反應","createTime":"2021-01-31T13:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T02:11:53.000Z","uid":258948,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6e8760ea1480337b3e2bcea97d1321722a2bbccb","tid":2388974,"uid":258948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/skSMJL4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FskSMJL4.png&h=b197a94c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/phK7tcL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FphK7tcL.png&h=326204f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gpCMJL6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgpCMJL6.png&h=d37ae9c3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xqVeSEs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxqVeSEs.png&h=804b9c52&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc19177453d60a06369f6ae0faa29389eb287f77","tid":2388974,"uid":76591,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:53:55.000Z","msg":"中國人唔傻，只係講太多真話會被刪post<br />\n中國官方佢地會用官方宣傳口吻去代替真實聲音，掩耳盜鈴。"},{"pid":"468d17c673d7af45e3c4650c753d8e9d9c644c5b","tid":2388974,"uid":389613,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:55:05.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">香港人用 BNO 係搬石頭砸中共春袋</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原來用 BNO 離開係 Trump 一早 set 左比中共既計時炸彈！我地更應該繼承 Trump 既精神，用 BNO 逼 Biden 同中共開戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"red\"> 只要有大批香港人離開，會造成現時已經虛弱既經濟徹底崩潰，而中共強行鎖國則引來百國聯軍。</span><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本１：支共反制 BNO 引致百國聯軍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> &gt; <ins>香港獨立戰爭</ins><br />\n<br />\n[武俠小說] 因為 BNO 香港變成外交博奕戰場！Trump 偷偷地幫香港插左支定海神針迫 Biden 打柒中共！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2377934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2377934</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本２：支共比 BNO 走引致經濟崩潰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> &gt; <ins>支共無錢發難</ins><br />\n<br />\n[神話故事] 中共經濟末日狂奔，BNO 就係大衛與歌利亞決戰粒石頭。港人出走成就 Trump 滅共偉業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2380593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2380593</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本２A：支共無錢發難引致世界大戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> &gt; <ins>香港獨立戰爭</ins><br />\n<br />\n[軍事小說] 習近平氏の希特拉化！英美德法荷日印澳同盟國形成！普京：依家局勢好似二戰前既30年代！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gCmQrS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gCmQrS</a><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n不論你係撐 Trump 既手足、定係支持滅共既手足，今次 BNO Visa 係時候身體力行，用你對腳投票去支持 Trump 呢條滅共戰線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">多你一個好多，少你一個唔掂！你既決定將會成為世界走向正義定係腐敗既關鍵因素！</span>"},{"pid":"049f2decfae9ee41baac76d39582c2f79b77cf01","tid":2388974,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:57:01.000Z","msg":"港共最驚人走 (有冇錢都驚人走)<br />\n香港人有得走就好走"},{"pid":"83085d231c8ef731b7fd50fa6af77acc4f0fd092","tid":2388974,"uid":258948,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fc19177453d60a06369f6ae0faa29389eb287f77","tid":2388974,"uid":76591,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:53:55.000Z","msg":"中國人唔傻，只係講太多真話會被刪post<br />\n中國官方佢地會用官方宣傳口吻去代替真實聲音，掩耳盜鈴。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:57:12.000Z","msg":"老胡已成condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老胡怎麼看<br />\n老胡怎麼看<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ce66efbd31e34ee66376bc87c3d86dea3c711b","tid":2388974,"uid":38177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:58:11.000Z","msg":"支那狗教人做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750e49135f0ced5117c451a1087b7faf3d6a8136","tid":2388974,"uid":301989,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"